skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guess the wrestler
des:
This is an interesting guessing game for all lovers of professional wrestling.

It features your famous male and female superstar wrestlers. You can either choose the male or female category to begin.

Under these two categories, you can choose to guess the theme songs or theme titles.

You are asked to guess the name of the wrestler by listening to a brief version of his/her theme songs or by just simply hearing the song title.

When users guess the wrestlers theme songs or theme title they move to the next question.

You think you know your wrestlers? Play Guess the Wrestler!!!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
